msgid "tardegy"
msgstr "tardegy"

#: ../../T/tardegy.rst:7
msgid "tar´d­jee, n\\."
msgstr "tar´d­jee, 名詞"

#: ../../T/tardegy.rst:9
msgid ""
"[deliberate mangling of tragedy] An incident in which someone who clearly "
"deserves to be selected out of the gene pool on grounds of extreme stupidity"
" meets with a messy end. Coined on the Darwin list, which is dedicated to "
"chronicling such incidents; but almost all hackers would instantly recognize"
" the intention of the term and laugh."
msgstr ""
"[tragedy(悲劇)の意図的な改変]極度の愚かさゆえに明らかに遺伝子プールから取り除かれて当然の者が、無残な最期を遂げる出来事。そうした出来事を記録することに専念するDarwinリストで造られたが、ほとんどすべてのハッカーはこの用語の意図を即座に認識して笑うだろう。"
